<h1>Register types</h1>

<div class="grid">
  <div class="grid__item three-fifths lap-two-thirds palm-one-whole">
    <p class="lead">The Register type is a two-letter code that indicates the source of a record.</p>
    <p>WinREG appends the register type code to the name of the church, e.g., "All Saints PR" would indicate the parish register of All Saints church.  When using Flexible CSV, the register type has its own field, register_type.</p>
    
  </div>	
  
